{"tid":2211991,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"想請教下做緊/有志老師既各位","createTime":"2020-09-21T12:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T13:44:29.000Z","uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f31f605e5ba88dbd2478f3943058fd8d1634516b","tid":2211991,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:37:33.000Z","msg":"我以前細個個時諗如果學生突然會受生命威脅時 例如被開槍擊中，被人行刺時，老師會唔會捨身救學生而食子彈同被人桶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想請教下做緊/有志老師既各位會唔會咁樣做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7361dba7322133e980b508667e500e0afc57323","tid":2211991,"uid":135040,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:39:38.000Z","msg":"我覺得幫學生走但係職責<br />\n但係講到擋子彈，我覺得唔擋都唔會有太多人話你<br />\n當然，點都有啲on9覺得應該要無私到條命都冇埋先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cac34430944440f773adbe3fb9d2b60b419574","tid":2211991,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"打份工啫<br />\n你老母都未必幫你擋啦"},{"pid":"81300ce37a22d200d39713e3a1f402ef5507671b","tid":2211991,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78cac34430944440f773adbe3fb9d2b60b419574","tid":2211991,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"打份工啫<br />\n你老母都未必幫你擋啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"我老母話會幫我檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e196b80ef7dd683bb819ebcf0df022c23dd036","tid":2211991,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81300ce37a22d200d39713e3a1f402ef5507671b","tid":2211991,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78cac34430944440f773adbe3fb9d2b60b419574","tid":2211991,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"打份工啫<br />\n你老母都未必幫你擋啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T13:13:55.000Z","ms